---
// CustomerSegments.astro
---
<section class="section" id="customers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">🏦 Who It's For</div>
      <h2>Built for institutions where<br/>the stakes are real.</h2>
      <p>We're not selling to every bank. We're solving a specific problem for institutions caught between AI innovation and regulatory accountability.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="segments-grid">
      <!-- Segment 1: Beachhead -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--primary" id="segment-banks">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">⭐ Primary Market</span>
          <span class="segment-years">Years 1–3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🏦</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Tier 1.5 & Tier 2 Banks</h3>
            <p class="segment-sub">$50B – $500B in assets</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="segment-jurisdictions">
          <span class="badge badge-amber">EU — DORA / ECB</span>
          <span class="badge badge-blue">US — SR 26-2 / Fed</span>
          <span class="badge badge-blue">UK — PRA</span>
          <span class="badge badge-blue">CA — OSFI</span>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why">Face the same punitive regulatory pressure as Mega-Banks, but lack the 10,000-person engineering army to build governance infrastructure in-house. <strong>Structurally forced to buy.</strong></p>

        <div class="segment-tam">
          <div class="tam-stat">
            <span class="tam-num">~314</span>
            <span class="tam-label">Total addressable institutions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tam-stat">
            <span class="tam-num">$3M+</span>
            <span class="tam-label">Target ARR by Year 3</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="segment-personas">
          <div class="persona-label">Decision-Making Unit</div>
          <div class="persona-list">
            <div class="persona-item">
              <span class="persona-role">🔥 Champion</span>
              <span class="persona-title">Head of AI Platform / VP of Risk Engineering</span>
              <span class="persona-pain">Their AI is built and blocked</span>
            </div>
            <div class="persona-item">
              <span class="persona-role">💰 Economic Buyer</span>
              <span class="persona-title">VP of Enterprise Architecture</span>
              <span class="persona-pain">Holds infrastructure budget</span>
            </div>
            <div class="persona-item">
              <span class="persona-role">🛑 Veto</span>
              <span class="persona-title">Chief Risk Officer (CRO)</span>
              <span class="persona-pain">Personal DORA liability — the real blocker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Segment 2: FinTechs -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--secondary" id="segment-fintechs">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">Secondary Market</span>
          <span class="segment-years">Year 2+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🚀</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Regulated FinTechs</h3>
            <p class="segment-sub">The "Speedboats"</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="segment-jurisdictions">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">Cloud-Native</span>
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">API-First</span>
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">OTel-Native</span>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why">Modern, heavily funded FinTechs, payments processors, and digital-only banks. They buy with engineering-driven POCs. Fast decisions, minimal bureaucracy.</p>

        <div class="fintech-names">
          <span class="fintech-name">Digital banks</span>
          <span class="fintech-name">Payments processors</span>
          <span class="fintech-name">Embedded finance</span>
        </div>

        <div class="segment-personas">
          <div class="persona-label">Decision-Making Unit</div>
          <div class="persona-list">
            <div class="persona-item">
              <span class="persona-role">💰 Buyer</span>
              <span class="persona-title">CTO / VP Engineering</span>
              <span class="persona-pain">Signs off after successful POC</span>
            </div>
            <div class="persona-item">
              <span class="persona-role">🔥 Champion</span>
              <span class="persona-title">Lead ML Engineer / Head of Data Platform</span>
              <span class="persona-pain">Runs the integration POC</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sales-cycle">
          <span class="mono">POC-to-contract:</span>
          <span class="cycle-time">3–6 months</span>
          <span class="cycle-vs">vs. 9–18 months for banks</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Excluded segment -->
    <div class="excluded-segment">
      <div class="excluded-inner">
        <span class="excluded-icon">🚫</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Explicitly Out of Scope: Quant Hedge Funds</strong>
          <p>Extreme data sovereignty paranoia, 100% air-gapped deployments, and no off-the-shelf SaaS adoption. A distraction for a seed-stage startup — revisit in Year 4+.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.segments-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.segment-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.segment--primary {
  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, rgba(0,212,255,0.02) 100%);
}

.segment-badge {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.segment-years {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
}

.segment-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.segment-icon { font-size: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.segment-header h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
.segment-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.segment-jurisdictions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

.segment-why { font-size: 0.9rem; }
.segment-why strong { color: var(--color-cyan); }

.segment-tam {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.tam-num {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-cyan);
  display: block;
  line-height: 1;
}
.tam-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.segment-personas { margin-top: auto; }
.persona-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.persona-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.persona-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
  gap: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}
.persona-role { font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); font-size: 0.75rem; }
.persona-title { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 500; }
.persona-pain { color: var(--color-text-dim); grid-column: 2; font-size: 0.72rem; margin-top: -0.25rem; }

.fintech-names { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.fintech-name {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  background: var(--color-surface-2);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-full);
}

.sales-cycle {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.cycle-time { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-green); font-size: 1rem; }
.cycle-vs { color: var(--color-text-dim); font-size: 0.72rem; }

/* Excluded */
.excluded-segment {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.excluded-inner {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.excluded-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.excluded-segment strong {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.excluded-segment p { font-size: 0.82rem; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .segments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .persona-item { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; }
  .persona-pain { grid-column: unset; }
}
</style>
